Name: Moto G5 Plus
Description: Moto G5 is a series of Android smartphones developed by Motorola Mobility, a subsidiary of Lenovo; it is the fifth generation of the Moto G family.

Name: Samsung J7 Prime
Description: The Samsung Galaxy J7 is an entry level smartphone released by Samsung in 2016 with 14 nm processor technology.

Name: Apple iPhone 6 Gold
Description: The iPhone 6 and iPhone 6 Plus are smartphones designed and marketed by Apple Inc. The devices are part of the iPhone series and were announced on September 9, 2014, and released on September 19, 2014.

Name: Lenovo Yoga Tab 3 (16 GB) 8 inch
Description: The Lenovo Yoga Tab 3 (8-inch) is powered by 1.3GHz quad-core Qualcomm Snapdragon 210 processor and it comes with 1GB of RAM. The tablet packs 16GB of internal storage that can be expanded up to 128GB via a microSD card.

Name: Dan Brown's Origin
Description: Origin is a 2017 science fiction mystery thriller novel by American author Dan Brown. and the fifth installment in his Robert Langdon series, following Angels & Demons, The Da Vinci Code, The Lost Symbol, and Inferno.

Name: Between the world and me
Description: Between the World and Me is a 2015 book written by Ta-Nehisi Coates and published by Spiegel & Grau.

Name: Exit west
Description: Exit West is a novel published in 2017, written by Pakistani author Mohsin Hamid. This is Hamid's fourth novel. The main themes of the novel are emigration and refugee problems.

Name: Station Eleven
Description: Station Eleven is a 2014 science fiction novel by Emily St. John Mandel. It is Mandel's fourth novel.

Name: Usha Ei 1602 dry iron
Description: Nothing can boost your confidence better than wearing neatly pressed clean clothes. Now iron your clothes right at your home anytime you want with this dry iron from Usha.

Name: Ortan Electric Kettle
Description: Boil water in a matter of minutes for baby food or make a steaming cup of fragrant tea with the 1.8L Ortan Electric kettle. Beautifully crafted and featuring a stainless-steel body, this kettle is perfect for your kitchen or office pantry.

Name: Morphy Richards Sm 3006 Electric Toaster
Description: The Morphy Richards Sandwich Maker SM3006(G)SS 700W is a perfect choice of appliance for any kitchen setting. This toaster is designed with non stick plates that are easy to clean and also offer a healthy cooking option.

Name: Bajaj Microwave Oven
Description: The Bajaj 1000 TSS 10-Litre Oven Toaster Grill is a classic approach to modern cooking. Its Element Selection option and 0-250 degree thermostat range make this multi-functional counter top oven a valuable addition to any kitchen.
